{"tid":482572,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"意籍攝影師鏡頭下的西環碼頭 紀錄一個個來到拍照的人","createTime":"2017-11-28T09:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T04:04:03.000Z","uid":12599,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f8ea666eb6df88079f759f11cfd82c8abd0a93","tid":482572,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"攝影師 Pierfrancesco Celada「Happiness Onthemove Award 2017」得獎作品：<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier1.jpg&h=73abfced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「西環碼頭」本名為「西區公眾貨物裝卸區」，位於香港島石塘咀干諾道西與山道之交匯處以西的海旁。該處並非休憩空間，但因為地方舒適，成為了附近居民的公共空間，加上可以欣賞日落，近年吸引了很多區外市民特意前來拍照。此外，由於路面凹凸不平，下雨後形成水窪，也有不少人來拍攝「天空之鏡」。西環碼頭近年為了香港熱門打卡地點之一，在 Instagram 上甚至被網民稱為「Instagram Pier」。<br />\n<br />\n意籍攝影師 Pierfrancesco Celada 在 2016 年 11 月開設了一個名為「insta_pier」的 Instagram 帳號，幾乎每天都會紀錄一個個來到西環碼頭的市民。有的人在自拍、有的人在拍結婚照或畢業照、也有的人跟朋友跳起拍照，大家都在同一個地方，做著不同的事情。<br />\n<br />\nPierfrancesco Celada 的作品：<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier2.jpg&h=fd24fb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier14.jpg&h=ec9c5c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier13.jpg&h=e659551e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier12.jpg&h=2af35580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier11.jpg&h=a47c5263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier10.jpg&h=68d652fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier9.jpg&h=a04ee758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier8.jpg&h=6ce4e7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier7.jpg&h=b5c4f56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier6.jpg&h=796ef5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier5.jpg&h=f7e1f217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier4.jpg&h=3b4bf289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier3.jpg&h=318efb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier16.jpg&h=aeb95b7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/insta_pier15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Finsta_pier15.jpg&h=20365c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府近年提出「西區海濱概念性總體規劃」，以「打造香港海港西大門新地標」為目標，將碼頭區改建成特色市集及海上噴泉公園，引來不少民間聲音反對，認為只會令獨特的西環碼頭淪為一式一樣的公園。<br />\n<br />\n從 Pierfrancesco Celada 的 IG 照片可以見到，市民都自由地享用這片空間，西環碼頭的魅力正在於其自然而然的環境，硬要加入管理，就會失去特質了。正如西環碼頭贏得「香港公共空間大獎 2013」的「由市民開創的空間大獎」時，評審會所言：「雖然只是空地、沒有甚麼設施，但卻讓市民能有無敵海景之餘，更能無拘無束地享用空間，進行不同類型的活動，其自由度乃是貨物裝卸區今次得獎的最大原因。」"},{"pid":"11a6beaa40c50c89870cca79291e6fd1f0c6a48d","tid":482572,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港共唔係差隻手埋黎啦臭手<br />\n掂邊樣衰邊樣"},{"pid":"e93492529ed2a3713f492e9bf7f96f5d2800ca69","tid":482572,"uid":60074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"好鬼鐘意睇啲影人影相既相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80cbb56ac9af8b206949098ff7752d8e490a406","tid":482572,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港共唔係差隻手埋黎啦臭手<br />\n掂邊樣衰邊樣</blockquote><br />\n一起左圍攔就已經唔係果回事"},{"pid":"b3c19a76fe16892b2d83182dbce9f351cba98364","tid":482572,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0a698e01db8759775509e0b129da8580f5fde6","tid":482572,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"唉～幾時又有人成功爭取&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c01dd5519e792e01239ac980d7853e91d75caf6","tid":482572,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"好好笑"},{"pid":"717a2ffc9f289be111d4c5f186dbd182c3682b92","tid":482572,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T21:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"053a89a7ddc813eea742f1405e621379fa74becb","tid":482572,"uid":35045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉～幾時又有人成功爭取&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經有，準備起菜園"},{"pid":"82fc71fd982f1253dcf97d61530f7a9a23faf0cb","tid":482572,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"海邊起花圃 真係唔知邊個天才諗出黎"},{"pid":"3138616fe6ffb8354dabdbd33c1329865b41b357","tid":482572,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鬼鐘意睇啲影人影相既相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}